---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { profile } from "../data/profile";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Research"
  description="Research interests of Wei Yang, a mathematics Ph.D. student at Peking University."
>
  <article class="page" aria-labelledby="research-title">
    <p class="eyebrow">Research</p>
    <h1 id="research-title">Research Interests</h1>

    <p>
      My current interests are in homotopy theory and arithmetic geometry,
      especially in questions where ideas from the two subjects interact. I am
      interested in homotopical structures that arise in arithmetic and
      geometric contexts.
    </p>

    <p>
      I am also interested in using techniques from arithmetic geometry to study
      problems in homotopy theory. More broadly, I am drawn to situations where
      arithmetic, geometric, and cohomological methods help clarify structural
      questions in homotopy theory.
    </p>

    <p>
      This page will be updated as my research projects, seminar talks, and
      preprints become available.
    </p>

    <section aria-labelledby="areas-title">
      <h2 id="areas-title">Areas</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Homotopy theory</li>
        <li>Arithmetic geometry</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <p class="muted">
      For research correspondence, please write to
      {profile.emailDisplay}.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
